<p>handlebars</p>
<ol>
  <li>npm install &#8211;save hbs</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">app.set('view engine', 'hbs');</code>:
    <ul>
      <li>sets which templating library to use (&quot;engine extension&quot;)</li>
      <li>http://expressjs.com/en/api.html#app.settings.table</li>
      <li>A template engine enables you to use static template files in your application. At runtime, the template engine replaces variables in a template file with actual values, and transforms the template into an HTML file sent to the client</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">req.set</code> - sets a header</li>
</ol>
